videos.headline: Minnesota picks off Penn State early
videos.description: Minnesota cornerback Antoine Winfield Jr. intercepts Penn State quarterback Sean Clifford early in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Minnesota picks off Penn State early) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Minnesota strikes first with 66-yard TD
videos.description: Minnesota quarterback Tanner Morgan finds Rashod Bateman for the 66-yard touchdown as Minnesota takes the early 7-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Minnesota strikes first with 66-yard TD) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brown breaks free for Penn State TD
videos.description: Journey Brown takes it to the house for the 45-yard touchdown as Penn State ties the game at 7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brown breaks free for Penn State TD) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Autman-Bell eludes defenders for the TD
videos.description: Minnesota quarterback Tanner Morgan finds Chris Autman-Bell on the screen-pass, and Bell takes it for a 21-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Autman-Bell eludes defenders for the TD) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Winfield Jr. picks off Clifford again
videos.description: Antoine Winfield Jr. intercepts Sean Clifford for the second time during the first half of Minnesota's matchup with Penn State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Winfield Jr. picks off Clifford again) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Morgan threads the needle for the Minnesota TD
videos.description: Tanner Morgan drops a dime down the sideline for Tyler Johnson who takes it for the 38-yard Minnesota touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Morgan threads the needle for the Minnesota TD) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clifford zips a TD to Bowers to cut Minnesota's lead
videos.description: Sean Clifford finds Nick Bowers for a 10-yard touchdown touchdown as Penn State draws close to Minnesota.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clifford zips a TD to Bowers to cut Minnesota's lead) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Green keeps for the Minnesota TD
videos.description: Minnesota QB Seth Green rushes for a 1-yard touchdown as Minnesota increases its lead over Penn State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Green keeps for the Minnesota TD) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brown's TD draws Penn State closer in 4th quarter
videos.description: Penn State won't give up as Journey Brown rushes six yards for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Howden's INT seals it for Minnesota
videos.description: Sean Clifford's pass is intercepted in the end zone by Jordan Howden as Minnesota hangs on to take down Penn State 31-26.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Howden's INT seals it for Minnesota) 2019/11/09 ESHEET
